@page "/"

<PageTitle>Human Capital Management System Demo</PageTitle>

<div class="hr-dashboard-center">
    <div class="hr-dashboard-welcome">
        <h1>
            <span class="wave">👋</span> Welcome to the HCM Demo App
        </h1>
        <h3>
            Human Capital Management made simple for teams
        </h3>
        <p>
            This demo application shows core HR workflows—built with .NET and Blazor, and wired for analytics with Grafana.
        </p>
        <ul class="demo-highlights">
            <li>Manage employees, departments, and salaries</li>
            <li>Role-based access: HR Admin, Manager, and Employee features</li>
            <li>
                Update employee records and permissions:<br />
                <span style="font-size:0.98em;">
                    <b>HR Admins</b> can add, edit, or remove anyone, including managers.<br />
                    <b>Managers</b> can edit records of their own team only, but cannot remove or add other employees.<br />
                    <b>Employees</b> can view their own data.
                </span>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
            This is a prototype for learning, exploring, and testing HR management concepts.<br>
            Use the menus to try features for each role and see how permissions work.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
